OL,3,CBernardo Silva to leave Manchester
OL,4,CCity at end of season
OL,6,FBernardo Silva is to leave Manchester
OL,7,FCity at the end of the season, the
OL,8,Fclub have confirmed.
OL,10,FThe 31-year-old Portugal
OL,11,Finternational's hugely successful nine-
OL,12,Fyear spell at the Etihad Stadium,
OL,13,Fwhich has brought him 19 major
OL,14,Ftrophies to date, will draw to a close
OL,15,Fthis summer, as suggested by assistant
OL,16,Fmanager Pep Lijnders earlier this
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
