OL,3,CBernardo Silva to leave Manchester
OL,4,CCity at end of season
OL,6,FA statement on the club's official
OL,7,Fwebsite read: "Manchester City can
OL,8,Fconfirm Bernardo Silva will leave the
OL,9,Fclub this summer."
OL,11,F"The Portuguese playmaker joined City
OL,12,Fin 2017 and has gone on to make 451
OL,13,Fappearances during a glorious nine-
OL,14,Fyear stay with the Blues.
OL,16,F"The 31-year-old's contribution to our
OL,17,Fgreatest sustained period of success
OL,18,Fis incalculable.
OL,26,@oD@OOUqD@RO]sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776363051
OL,3,CBernardo Silva to leave Manchester
OL,4,CCity at end of season
OL,6,F"Bernardo will now focus on seeking to
OL,7,Ftry and ensure his remaining time at
OL,8,FCity ends with even more silverware,
OL,9,Fwith Pep Guardiola's side still very
OL,10,Fmuch in the hunt to win both the
OL,11,FPremier League title and the FA Cup.
OL,13,F"In short, he will be deservedly
OL,14,Fremembered both as one of City's
OL,15,Ffinest and most popular players of all
OL,16,Ftime."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
