OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776363051
OL,3,CBernardo Silva to leave Manchester
OL,4,CCity at end of season
OL,6,FSilva, a #43million signing from
OL,7,FMonaco in May 2017, has six Premier
OL,8,FLeague titles, one Champions League,
OL,9,Ftwo FA Cups, five Carabao Cups, Club
OL,10,FWorld Cup and European Super Cup
OL,11,Fwinner's medals among his haul.
OL,13,FConfirming the news, he wrote to the
OL,14,Fclub's fans on his Instagram account:
OL,15,F"When I arrived nine years ago, I was
OL,16,Ffollowing a dream of a little boy,
OL,17,Fwanting to succeed in life, wanting to
OL,18,Fachieve great things.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776363051
OL,3,CBernardo Silva to leave Manchester
OL,4,CCity at end of season
OL,6,F"This city and this club gave me much
OL,7,Fmore than that, much more than I ever
OL,8,Fhoped for. What we won and achieved
OL,9,Ftogether is a legacy that will forever
OL,10,Fbe cherished in my heart. The
OL,11,FCenturions, the domestic quadruple,
OL,12,Fthe Treble, the Four In A Row and much
OL,13,Fmore... It wasn't that bad.
OL,15,F"In a few months, it's time to say
OL,16,Fgoodbye to the city where not only we
OL,17,Fwon so much as a football club, but
OL,18,Falso where I started my marriage and
OL,19,Fmy family. From the bottom of my
OL,20,Fheart, Ines and Carlota, thank you!
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
