FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776363051
OL,3,CBernardo Silva to leave Manchester
OL,4,CCity at end of season
OL,6,F"To the fans, your unconditional
OL,7,Fsupport throughout the years is
OL,8,Fsomething that I will never forget. My
OL,9,Fmain goal as a player was to always
OL,10,Fplay with passion so you guys could
OL,11,Ffeel proud and well represented on the
OL,12,Fpitch. I hope you felt that every
OL,13,Fsingle game.
OL,15,F"I arrived as a Man City player, I
OL,16,Fleave as one more of you, a Man City
OL,17,Fsupporter for life. Keep supporting
OL,18,Fthis young team and I'm pretty sure
OL,19,Fthey will bring you a lot of new
OL,20,Ffantastic memories in the future.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776363051
OL,3,CBernardo Silva to leave Manchester
OL,4,CCity at end of season
OL,6,F"To the club, Pep, the staff and all
OL,7,Fmy team-mates these nine years, thank
OL,8,Fyou for all the memories and for
OL,9,Fletting me be a part of this journey
OL,10,Ffor so long. The atmosphere we created
OL,11,Fevery day in the training ground made
OL,12,Fme feel at home and a part of a big
OL,13,Ffamily. Let's enjoy together these
OL,14,Flast weeks and fight for what this
OL,15,Fseason still brings us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@XO]
